{"type": "article", "id": 51639, "title": "UA 涉嫌用户数据泄露，以及，Blue Bottle 开设京都首家店 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2018-03-30T03:56:47Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1060, "name": "H&M"}, {"id": 2147, "name": "Blue Bottle"}, {"id": 2634, "name": "Under Armour"}, {"id": 44164, "name": "Puma"}, {"id": 3133, "name": "Jil Sander"}, {"id": 2145, "name": "Converse"}, {"id": 3559, "name": "上海时装周"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 30, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180330114327Q75dVOloUwYsZWRf.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/technology/under-armour-fitness-app-data-breach-affects-millions-of-users-myfitnesspal-1202641439/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Under Armour 运动 App 涉嫌泄露 1.5 亿用户数据 </strong></a>| Under Armour 周四发布声明称，其运动 App MyFitnessPal 的 1.5 亿用户数据在上个月被泄露，包括用户名、邮箱地址、和加密的密码等信息均受影响，但未涉及用户的社保号码、驾驶证号和银行卡号等隐私信息。目前，Under Armour 称正在与一家数据安全公司合作调查此次事件，消息一出，公司的股价一度下跌 2.4%。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/activewear/puma-director-innovation-new-frontiers-biodesign-mit-design-lab-1202640496/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Puma 与 MIT 实验室合作，探究最新生物材料设计</strong></a> | 四月的米兰设计周上，Puma 将展示与麻省理工设计实验室共同开发的四个实验性产品，包括号称能个性化通风的“呼吸鞋”，通过生物反馈来提高运动员表现的“深度学习鞋垫”等。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>继在东京接连开了好几家店之后，<a href=\"https://casabrutus.com/food/71834\" rel=\"nofollow\">Blue Bottle&nbsp;</a>来到京都开设门店，这也是它迄今为止最大的一家日本门店。 </p><p>Blue Bottle 京都店改装自百年历史的京都町屋，由 Schemata 操刀设计，入口处被改造成了大面积的玻璃墙营造出通透感。另外，为了庆祝京都首家店的开幕，店铺推出了多款限定单品，比如帆布包、帽子、插花器等。 </p><p>这家店位于京都市左京区南禅寺草川町 64，去京都的时候不妨去看看。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330111502TAoDR1Ynw493c65e.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803301115117Zwqd51jkugNOzPD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330111514aquveUZNAlM6YkrX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330111706YuRz0jr7Icgiwkv4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665165\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330111654f6IRt9TVzGJqCA7X.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665165\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803301116546UQtSy9hbrekiYF2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665165\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330111654Uf3JKvPGCF5IR1np.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665165\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330111700CatxT71FezDmGUJb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665165\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330111700MkxYFUdOaCzpI5bV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665165\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>Jil Sander 发布了 2018 系列最新广告片，请来了德国导演 Wim Wenders 在五个不同的场景进行拍摄，画风还挺美的。</p><p>登陆 <a href=\"https://www.jilsander.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jil Sander </a>官网可以查看完整视频。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803301117402u3kOFqszK47WDA1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803301117400GjMmsSFTA59taNr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330111740B1n83r6kUJPGQKVg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330111740NkIdJgb98TxXi6oE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330111740Vj6cbnW3rNKhqsJF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330111741BWQvKTCOlzIgP5SG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330111744b9AlyJS18mU5NPwz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/jw-anderson-converse-new-classics-release-date-price/\" rel=\"nofollow\">J.W Anderson 和 Converse 的联名系列再出新品</a>。从老式的芭蕾舞鞋中汲取灵感，搭配针织鞋面及皮革细节，两双全新鞋款 Chuck 70 U-Throat Ballet 和 Chuck 70 XX Hi 售价分别为 120 和 160 美元，将于 4 月 4 日正式发售。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330111816Cu1h8TpDxBKRE2kJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330111816juHeGRd3nbzXLgam.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330111813HrtCMYnb4Oz7PS0f.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330111816jkoiyJ8UThFf5PIB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330111817XC02LQmFuBNZsfry.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330111816ap07ZBoYIQy6ndiz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330111817lVoJakO0xMvmtubA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330111812yB94dJDhfSzOo0R5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330111817LVathnv2i76W4IRK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330111814QZJR2YL0ycnGHtoC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330111813sIbUfBJD6TKMOawE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502347\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330111814Ms7Bm0kv9pJqUgZy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502347\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330111816Ozg3Xf5qemEad0lN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502347\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/592351\" rel=\"nofollow\">H&amp;M CONSCIOUS EXCLUSIVE </a>将于 4 月 18 日发布最新系列。<br></p><p>继天丝、天然亚麻、废弃塑料瓶等特殊材料之后，H&amp;M 这一次从废弃的渔业专用网中提取尼龙，用百分百再生的环保尼龙材料 ECONYL 制衣。在设计方面，这一季的灵感来自 20 世纪初瑞典艺术与手工业运动中活跃的艺术家夫妇 Karin &amp; Carl Larsson。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330113950nP5lrNDp3YGvO4ab.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330113952Nw8L9sPt61pO2CcD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330113954TNSC12KmnZWQUxjh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330113954U1hkQKzbO4y259SZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.712500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330113955cJbZKqYUI70y3Cpd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.848333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330113957Kw98Om1CkizrQEed.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330113958EZvngoxqemiU5krT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.705000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330114004va9YnOCWJyZjdI2V.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.707500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803301140045gzIeR7sXDQ6f93x.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.707500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330114004h5MQ9wbzWoNaKrnV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803301140056w5iaBHOyZR9G0YD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.709167\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>上海时装周继续更新。<br></p><p>主张用旧衣服创造新时尚的再造衣银行，这一季的主题是“别致的天真”。设计师张娜通过对复杂面料的减法处理，让舒适、宽松、有体量的轮廓成为本季设计的重心。 </p><p>另外，昨天的秀场也很有趣，设计师与艺术家小珂X子涵共同创作了“城市共生”主题，将秀场实验性地变成了一出“时光剧场”。邀请了生活在上海的普通人与家庭以及艺术家，让他们穿着再生面料与旧衣拼接的新时装讲述属于他们的故事。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330113146enXH7UMDV5a2rwuk.JPG\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330113147kfSs9K5cBvQi7DFA.JPG\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330113151Sl9nywXQRMaOusCF.JPG\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803301131547bcoRG8IlCLyKkx0.JPG\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330113155oqHD0mjP9Ugpuc1I.JPG\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330113155nzIaL9Q02cUqZtvy.JPG\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330113159z0ZdNAqx2Bp34iPJ.JPG\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330113207OHaRP83bsivSgLfy.JPG\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330113213PxyDJcQs2BdT1Rwt.JPG\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330113213wf3a4PhVrH6lEUGF.JPG\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330113213lcdUFG4w6ZCjQ1KR.JPG\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330113219m5avuHCqEV8BRnw0.JPG\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330113221OGIatN57vRuhKFJm.JPG\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330113222KmaIPg2NdqX91ALk.JPG\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180330113224Cj3Ifc5VHxsurziR.JPG\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：H&amp;M</p>"}